Source: libnemo-normalize
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Brian West <brian@mcalester.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), build-essential, g++, libfst-dev,
               autoconf, automake, libtool, pkg-config, dh-autoreconf
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: libnemo-normalize
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libnemo-normalize-data (= ${source:Version})
Description: NeMo text normalization via OpenFst - shared library
 A C/C++ shared library wrapping NVIDIA NeMo/OpenFst text normalization
 grammars. Provides a pure C API for text normalization (TN) and inverse
 text normalization (ITN) without requiring Python at runtime.

Package: libnemo-normalize-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libnemo-normalize (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: NeMo text normalization via OpenFst - development files
 Headers, static library, and pkg-config file for developing against
 libnemo-normalize.

Package: libnemo-normalize-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: NeMo text normalization via OpenFst - grammar data files
 Pre-exported FAR grammar files for NeMo text normalization covering
 19 languages across 28 grammar sets (12 TN + 16 ITN).
